text.tspan: Change in kaya identity: drivers of CO₂ emissions, World, 1965 to 2021
Percentage change in the four parameters of the Kaya Identity, which determine total CO₂ emissions. Emissions
include fossil fuel and industry emissions1 . Land use change is not included.
Source: Our World in Data based on Global Carbon Project; UN; BP; World Bank; Maddison Project Database
Note: GDP per capita is measured in 2011 international-$ (PPP). This adjusts for inflation and cross-country price differences.
